com.amplifyframework.api.graphql

Interface GraphQLResponse.Factory

  • Enclosing class:
    GraphQLResponse<R>

    public static interface GraphQLResponse.Factory
    A factory which generates a strongly-typed response object from a string that was returned from a GraphQL API.
